557
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:12,790
So you start sneaking into the station.

558
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,230
You're wrong.It wasn't like that...

559
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:16,760
come on,jenny.Your father let you down once,then twice.

