00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:18,270
Dottie was right. It was...it was no place for a kid.

588
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:20,150
I wouldn't have cared.

589
00:36:26,950 --> 00:36:30,900
How 'bout we take that trip to anywhere?

590
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:35,050
Let me make up for lost time.

591
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:38,690
What about your show?

592
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:43,560
I told 'em I was going to take a little time off to spend with my family.

593
00:36:51,870 --> 00:36:53,230
We talked about leaving in a couple of weeks.

594
00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:57,700
