597
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,340
I never told her.

598
00:37:07,860 --> 00:37:09,070
You sure?

599
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,220
Might get her upset.

600
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:14,410
That might even go talk to the hawk.

601
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:17,150
Try to stop him.

602
00:37:19,740 --> 00:37:23,450
Everything my mom did was because she loved me.

603
00:37:28,390 --> 00:37:31,770
I understand you and hawk had a daughter?

