641
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,790
You abandoned us.

642
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:55,080
You're a selfish son of a bitch,and you always will be.

643
00:39:55,090 --> 00:39:56,910
I'm not that man anymore.

